---
title: One-Pot Southwest Chicken Soup with Bulgur topped with Avocado & Scallions
description: This warming chicken soup is a true celebration of spices. A combo of our signature Southwest and Mexican spice blends deliver the smoky, savory flavors of cumin, garlic powder, chili powder, oregano, and more! The spices season chicken, tomato, and onion, then everything’s simmered with bulgur wheat for a hearty soup with a nutritious boost. To balance all that flavor, you’ll top things off with cooling avocado and fresh scallion greens. Basically, it’s all you avo wanted in a soup!
